('10821', '1', 'Fry the bacon over medium heat until barely crisp. Using kitchen scissors, snip the bacon into -inch pieces.'),
('10821', '2', 'Pour off all but 2 teaspoons fat from the pan.'),
('10821', '3', 'Add the shallots and saut until soft.'),
('10821', '4', 'Add the chicken broth, brown ale, orange juice and zest, and brown sugar and bring to a boil. Cook for 10 minutes on medium heat.'),
('10821', '5', 'Add the bacon and sprouts and cook for 10 minutes more, stirring frequently, until sprouts are coated with a thick sauce.'),
